OL,5,G0000 Heatwave
OL,6,     FDramatised documentary. An
OL,7,     Falarming vision of Britain caught
OL,8,     Fin the grip of an environmental
OL,9,     Fand social nightmare. It's summer
OL,10,     F2006, and temperatures have topped
OL,11,     F100 degrees, with no end in sight.
OL,12,G0130 Only Connect
OL,13,     F3/15. Quiz show in which
OL,14,     Fconnections must be made between
OL,15,     Fseemingly random subjects. Three
OL,16,     Fmembers of the Gay Men's Chorus
OL,17,     Fplay a trio of postgraduates.
